                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable H</hi> 42.) I apprehended the prisoner—he said he had seen the jacket on the prosecutor's back the day previous but had not seen it that morning.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I had seen a jacket on the prosecutor's back, but not that day.</p>
